OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdecades-old council tax    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbands                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Council tax bands in England should be 
OL,6, overhauled to fix a crisis in council  
OL,7, funding, a group representing northern 
OL,8, businesses has urged.                  
OL,10,FThe Northern Powerhouse Partnership    
OL,11,F(NPP) says the decades-old property    
OL,12,Fvaluations underpinning the bands      
OL,13,Fshould be redone to make them fairer.  
OL,15,FIt wants Chancellor Jeremy Hunt to     
OL,16,Fcommit to a national revaluation in    
OL,17,FMarch's Budget.                        
OL,19,FThe government says it has no plans for
OL,20,Fa nationwide band revaluation.         
